<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4A90D9;
    }
    .header h2 {
      color: #4A90D9;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .code-box {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .code {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4A90D9;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border: 2px dashed #4A90D9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #f0f6ff;
    }
    .tip {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>欢迎注册之间</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>尊敬的 <%= userEmail %>：</p>
      <p>您正在注册之间账号，您的验证码为：</p>
      <div class="code-box">
        <span class="code"><%= verifyCode %></span>
      </div>
      <p class="tip">验证码有效期为 15 分钟，请尽快完成注册。</p>
      <p class="tip">如非本人操作，请忽略此邮件。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
